  [2]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/10/docs/api/java/lang/Runnable.html
  [3]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/10/docs/api/java/util/concurrent/ExecutorService.html#shutdown()
  [4]: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coordinated_Universal_Time

